: thrust = hover_throttle (too high) → drone jumps up
- Frame 2: err_z is now positive (drone above target), vel.z
[/THINK]
[2026-06-12T13:29:28.736Z] [THINK]
 is positive (moving up)
  - target_acc_z_pid = Kp*err - Kd*vel (both negative since
